{"tid":390849,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人愈大 對生活愈無奈","createTime":"2017-09-07T10:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T11:23:07.000Z","uid":52339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ac206eeb34d7830d3904c68010dcb0b61b76ac91","tid":390849,"uid":52339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:50:15.000Z","msg":"屋企唔有錢收入唔高 唯有自己生性啲番多啲part time <br />\n為既係唔洗屋企人咁辛苦搵錢 亦都盡量慳住洗<br />\n一個月番到盡一盡先6 7000蚊<br />\n儲左一年先夠錢去個小旅行<br />\n<br />\n點撚知聽到人地每年拎保良局幾萬蚊助學金<br />\n明明成績勁差 就係因為住過宿舍 就有社工幫手<br />\n再加埋學資處全額補助 年年都有成十萬揸手<br />\n年年去幾次旅行都無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明明啲錢唔關自己事 但聽完之後就覺得好頹 <br />\n究竟自己咁辛苦番工為左啲乜 <br />\n<br />\n不過算啦 訓醒咪又要番工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b3905d3b988a002f417786d59b7c61c63496ee","tid":390849,"uid":121349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T11:08:45.000Z","msg":"忠忠直直終需乞食"},{"pid":"cb02dbf7ac9da39b9aace0b2409c44d6e555ad1b","tid":390849,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T11:09:23.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"e6bafb4cc43e3d7396a067ed613dc59745fce4eb","tid":390849,"uid":52339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T11:23:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>忠忠直直終需乞食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咬老綜收入仲好過辛辛苦苦番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}